[vc_row row_type="1" video_fullscreen="true" blox_bg_attachment="false" blox_cover="true" blox_repeat="no-repeat" blox_dark="false" parallax_speed="6" process_count="3" video_type="video/youtube" video_pattern="true" maxslider_parallax="true" maxslider_pattern="true"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][rev_slider_vc alias="wedding-jasmine-slider"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="0" row_id="couple" video_fullscreen="true" blox_bg_attachment="false" blox_cover="true" blox_repeat="no-repeat" blox_dark="false" parallax_speed="6" process_count="3" video_type="video/youtube" video_pattern="true" maxslider_parallax="true" maxslider_pattern="true"][vc_column width="1/1"][distance type="4"][maxtitle type="jasmine" heading="2" secondtitle="US" description="Meet our perfect bride and groom"]ABOUT[/maxtitle][distance type="3"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][brideorgroom gender="bride" type="jasmine" img="23" name="MAGGIE CARTER" text="We were dating, and I felt and still do feel, the happiest girl in the world. Joshua makes me feel so special and loved. You are the love of my life, my best friend. I don’t think anybody could be happier than I am today." first_social="twitter" first_url="#" second_social="facebook" second_url="#" third_social="google-plus" third_url="#" fourth_social="linkedin" fourth_url="#" link_text="MAGGIE’S PAGE" link_url="http://webnus.biz/themes/weddingsuite/jasmine/maggie/"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][brideorgroom gender="groom" type="jasmine" img="24" name="JOSHUA KENDALL" text="Maggie and I first met in Bristol. I’m sure she must have thought my fashion sense quite strange, especially as at the time I was wearing a bright orange hammock. The thing you hang between two trees to sleep on." first_social="twitter" first_url="#" second_social="facebook" second_url="#" third_social="google-plus" third_url="#" fourth_social="linkedin" fourth_url="#" link_text="JOSHUA’S PAGE" link_url="http://webnus.biz/themes/weddingsuite/jasmine/joshua/"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="0" row_id="story" video_fullscreen="true" blox_bg_attachment="false" blox_cover="true" blox_repeat="no-repeat" blox_dark="false" parallax_speed="6" process_count="3" video_type="video/youtube" video_pattern="true" maxslider_parallax="true" maxslider_pattern="true"][vc_column][distance type="3"][maxtitle type="jasmine" heading="2" secondtitle="LOVE STORY" description="Read and follow the story of how we fall in love"]OUR[/maxtitle][distance type="2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="68" css_animation="left-to-right" style="vc_box_rounded" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][distance type="4"][vc_column_text]

OUR FIRST DATING STORY

Days passed one by one and we used to meet each other every day in the office. I used to come to his room to ask questions and I was so happy about it. Then one day he asked me to go out with him, although it was not an easy move but he should take his chance! “Why not J, I love to come with you. A dinner is a perfect idea for me”, I said to Joshua. Since that first wonderful day we've spent every weekend together.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]
“Why not J, I love to come with you. A dinner is a perfect idea for me” _Maggie Carter 23 aug 2014
[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][vc_single_image image="72" style="vc_box_rounded" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][distance type="1"][vc_column_text]

HOW WE MET EACH OTHER

It took about two months to plan my marriage proposal to Maggie, my girlfriend of three and a half years. We’re both designers, working in a same company. She came to work 4 years ago and my boss asked me to guide her to her room and get familiar with the office. Like movies and as they say love in first sight, yes it happened! Later Maggie said to me that she liked me too. “You were so cute and funny for me, I never had a same feeling for someone before”, she said. We became best friends then.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]
“You were so cute and funny for me, I never had a same feeling for someone before” _Maggie Carter 19 sep 2014
[/vc_column_text][distance type="2"][vc_single_image image="707" alignment="right" style="vc_box_rounded" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full" css_animation="right-to-left"][distance type="3"][vc_column_text]

OUR INGAGEMENT

It was Saturday, April 26, 2014. I knew that it was the big day! I started off that normal Saturday by taking Maggie to her favorite restaurants. We went and all was completely normal up until the fortune cookies came out. I made sure Maggie took that fortune cookie. Once she opened it, she found the saying, “Will You Marry Me?” I was shocked when Joshua proposed me. I said yes, why not? He was a man who makes me happiest woman on the earth forever.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]
“Will You Marry Me?” _Joshua Kendall 15 dec 2014
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column][distance type="4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="0" row_id="ceremony" video_fullscreen="true" blox_bg_attachment="false" blox_cover="true" blox_repeat="no-repeat" blox_dark="false" parallax_speed="6" process_count="3" video_type="video/youtube" video_pattern="true" maxslider_parallax="true" maxslider_pattern="true"][vc_column width="1/1"][distance type="1"][maxtitle type="jasmine" heading="2" secondtitle="CEREMONY" description="Event when, where and how information"]MAIN[/maxtitle][distance type="1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

We like everything on the wedding day be perfect! We made a great plan for this day! The location and details all for this big day can be found below. Thanks so much for all our family members and friends [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][infobox icon_name="li_calendar" title="DATE AND LOCATION"]It will be held on monday July 23, 2015 @ ST.AUGUSTINE church, 130 Ohua ave. Honolulu, HI 96815 US Check the map for directions. [/infobox][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][infobox icon_name="li_clock" title="TIME"]The wedding ceremony will begin @ 10:00 A.M on ST.AUGUSTINE church. Lunch will be after the ceremony with drink and light music.[/infobox][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][infobox icon_name="fa-bicycle" title="ACCOMMODATION"]-Ewa Hotel Waikiki @ 5000 Kahala Avenue -Pacific Beach Hotel @ 1956 Ala Moana Boulevard -Aston Waikiki Sunset @ 1956 Ala Moana Boulevard[/infobox][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][gmap zoom="16" marker="enable" maptype="ROADMAP" width="0" height="400" address="ST.AUGUSTINE church, 130 Ohua ave. Honolulu, HI 96815 US"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][distance type="4"][maxtitle type="jasmine" heading="2" secondtitle="BIG DAY" description="We are counting down every seconds till the 23 July 2015"]UNTIL OUR[/maxtitle][countdown type="jasmine" datetime="7/1/2015" done="Finished"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="0" row_id="party" video_fullscreen="true" blox_bg_attachment="false" blox_cover="true" blox_repeat="no-repeat" blox_dark="false" parallax_speed="6" process_count="3" video_type="video/youtube" video_pattern="true" maxslider_parallax="true" maxslider_pattern="true"][vc_column width="1/1"][maxtitle type="jasmine" heading="2" secondtitle="PARTY" description="Event when, where and how information"]WEDDING[/maxtitle][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Guests always love the energy of a live band but tend to want to hear the original artist sing their favorite tunes. Maggie may hire a dance band but also play DJ'ed music during the breaks, "We've talked with a band called The Infusion Experience," heart beats" The DJ plays the original music while the percussion players play live. It's a huge crowd pleaser! [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][infobox icon_name="li_calendar" title="DATE AND LOCATION"]It will be held on Monday July 23, 2015 @ Kuhio Beach Park, Honolulu, HI 96815 US Check the map for directions.[/infobox][distance type="1"][infobox icon_name="li_clock" title="TIME"]The wedding party will begin @ 18:00 P.M on Kuhio Beach park. Free drinks and music is on the way, no costume is needed.[/infobox][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][gmap zoom="16" marker="enable" maptype="ROADMAP" width="0" height="426" address="Kuhio Beach Park, Honolulu, HI 96815 US"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_gallery type="flexslider_slide" interval="3" images="790,789,788" onclick="link_no" custom_links_target="_self" img_size="full"][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

[icon name="li_shop" size="34px" color="#e41f1f"] LOCAL ATTRACTIONS

Big love, Joshua and Maggie xoxo

item.title: Wedding consulting
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column width="7/12"][vc_column_text]

Wedding consulting

Weddings are significant events in people's lives and as such, couples are often willing to spend considerable amount of money to ensure that their weddings are well-organized. We will help you in this way.

 
  • Advice prospective brides in all phases of wedding planning, such as etiquette, attire of wedding party, and selection of trousseau: Compiles list of prospective brides from newspaper announcements of engagements.
  • Mails promotional material to offer own and store's services as consultant.
  • Recommends trousseau for bride, and costumes and accessories for attendants.
  • Advises bride on selection of silverware style and pattern, china, glassware, stationery, invitations, flowers, and catering service.
  • May display and sell wedding trousseau to bride and attire for attendants, and silverware, china, and glassware to brides and wedding gift purchasers, performing duties as described under SALESPERSON Master Title.
  • May compile and maintain gift register.
  • May arrange for photographers to take pictures of wedding party.
  • May attend rehearsals and wedding ceremony to give advice on etiquette.
  • May accompany bride when shopping in store or shop for her.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_single_image image="4826" alignment="center" border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
